OL,3,CLondon's Burning and Grange Hill actor
OL,4,CJohn Alford dies in prison
OL,6,FFormer London's Burning and Grange
OL,7,FHill actor John Alford has died in
OL,8,Fprison months after being jailed for
OL,9,Fsexually assaulting two teenage girls.
OL,11,FAlford, 54, was jailed for eight-and-a-
OL,12,Fhalf years in January after he was
OL,13,Ffound guilty of the assaults which
OL,14,Foccurred during a party at a friend's
OL,15,Fhome.
OL,17,FHe died at HMP Bure in Norfolk on
OL,18,FFriday, the Prison Service said.
