OL,3,CLondon's Burning and Grange Hill actor
OL,4,CJohn Alford dies in prison
OL,6,FThe former actor was convicted of four
OL,7,Fcounts of sexual activity with a 14-
OL,8,Fyear-old girl and charges of sexual
OL,9,Fassault and assault by penetration
OL,10,Frelating to a 15-year-old girl at a
OL,11,Fproperty in Hertfordshire on April 9
OL,12,F2022.
OL,14,FJurors heard during the trial that the
OL,15,Fdefendant, charged under his real name
OL,16,FJohn Shannon, sexually assaulted the
OL,17,Fgirls while they were drunk following
OL,18,Fa night out at the pub.
