OL,4,CJohn Alford dies in prison
OL,6,FA Prison Service spokesman said: "John
OL,7,FShannon died in prison on March 13
OL,8,F2026.
OL,10,F"As with all deaths in custody, the
OL,11,FPrisons and Probation Ombudsman will
OL,12,Finvestigate."
